sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant Service
    participant Database
    participant Cache

    User->>Frontend: Upload File
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/files
    API->>Service: Process Upload
    Service->>Database: Store Metadata
    Service->>Cache: Cache File Info
    Cache-->>Service: Cached Data
    Service-->>API: Upload Result
    API-->>Frontend: Response
    Frontend-->>User: Success Notification

    User->>Frontend: Start Reconciliation
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/reconciliation/jobs
    API->>Service: Create Job
    Service->>Database: Store Job
    Service->>Cache: Cache Job Status
    Service-->>API: Job Created
    API-->>Frontend: Job Response
    Frontend->>Frontend: WebSocket Listen
    Service->>Cache: Update Status
    Cache->>Frontend: WebSocket Update
    Frontend-->>User: Progress Update

